{"tid":1239162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【女子世盃】瘋狂犯規踢法粗野 中國女足被轟：無所不用其極！","createTime":"2019-06-18T05:31:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T05:55:00.000Z","uid":141151,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c997a4604cc60edaef36a8283d2c3446be7b24c3","tid":1239162,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:31:52.000Z","msg":"【女子世盃】瘋狂犯規踢法粗野 中國女足被轟：無所不用其極！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20190617/59727193\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190617%2F59727193&d=b2hjM7c23Ds3Tm%2B3KbcyARR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=db6f4a52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190617%2F59727193&h=46cda30e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20190617/59727193</a><br />\n<br />\n女子世盃B組最後一輪賽事，將於香港時間今晚零時零分上演，其中中國女足與西班牙女足賽前同得三分，兩隊將直接對撼爭奪出線權。惟賽前西班牙女足主帥維達（Jorge Vilda），在賽前記者會上表示，中國女足踢法總是破壞規則，是一支無所不用其極的球隊。<br />\n<br />\n中國女足在今屆女子世盃，首場對德國全場多達19次犯規，4名球員吃下黃牌，賽後已被德國傳媒炮轟踢法粗野；第二仗中國雖以1:0戰勝南非女足，但亦錄得12次犯規，兩場的犯規次數總和多達31次，是今屆女子世盃犯規次數最多的球隊。<br />\n<br />\n故在「生死戰」前夕，西班牙女足主帥維達稱：「中國是一支總是遊走在球例邊緣、一支無所不用其極的球隊，我們在之前兩場比賽都看到了，但我們知道怎樣應付，中國女足反擊及防守都很利害，我們會好好研究。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">消息傳出後內地網民隨即「玻璃心」爆發，直斥：「你們西班牙的馬德里體育會踢法乾淨嗎？論踢球髒誰及你們的沙治奧拉莫斯及迪亞高哥斯達？」、「我看這個西班牙教練是有病，把中國當作南韓看待，中國踢球一向老實。」、「今晚西班牙不許犯規！」等。</span>"},{"pid":"486bbb9e9cea0f8ae5ff4546b01fca66646a8616","tid":1239162,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f270ba7857706cdc22ab48f6bd9d71e95ad9bf08","tid":1239162,"uid":69746,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:42:50.000Z","msg":"叫香港d狗官落去踢啦 佢地傳波好叻"},{"pid":"20baba4458479464b74e8cb67ccb21f492496d04","tid":1239162,"uid":114196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:45:18.000Z","msg":"魔鬼隊"},{"pid":"fc646289f3525623d71adaa012718e73b758b60a","tid":1239162,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f270ba7857706cdc22ab48f6bd9d71e95ad9bf08","tid":1239162,"uid":69746,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:42:50.000Z","msg":"叫香港d狗官落去踢啦 佢地傳波好叻"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:45:43.000Z","msg":"但係個個都剩係識俾直線無人接波呢"},{"pid":"26d993f6388d765a211049e0fd4f272cdc7beaf3","tid":1239162,"uid":169484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f270ba7857706cdc22ab48f6bd9d71e95ad9bf08","tid":1239162,"uid":69746,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:42:50.000Z","msg":"叫香港d狗官落去踢啦 佢地傳波好叻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:47:27.000Z","msg":"佢哋射波叻啫<br />\n鬼識做同組織"},{"pid":"788e624b3d40faa2b3b4426da74c188c02166679","tid":1239162,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc646289f3525623d71adaa012718e73b758b60a","tid":1239162,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f270ba7857706cdc22ab48f6bd9d71e95ad9bf08","tid":1239162,"uid":69746,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:42:50.000Z","msg":"叫香港d狗官落去踢啦 佢地傳波好叻"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:45:43.000Z","msg":"但係個個都剩係識俾直線無人接波呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:47:53.000Z","msg":"犯規都叻"},{"pid":"c3e2d63ce30af090b3cbb1c1a89f8b4b508e9b71","tid":1239162,"uid":41317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc646289f3525623d71adaa012718e73b758b60a","tid":1239162,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f270ba7857706cdc22ab48f6bd9d71e95ad9bf08","tid":1239162,"uid":69746,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:42:50.000Z","msg":"叫香港d狗官落去踢啦 佢地傳波好叻"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:45:43.000Z","msg":"但係個個都剩係識俾直線無人接波呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T05:48:07.000Z","msg":"咩冇人接<br />\n冇得你唔接添呀<br />\n個波拉住西咁